name: The CouponDoc
overview: TheCouponDoc.com is a website that enables users to retrieve discounts on their prescriptions as well as their over the counter drugs. The site takes the fragmented pharmaceutical coupon market and puts all of the content on one website where a user can search for their medicine and find all available coupons / discounts as well as a side by side cost comparison to all of its competitors. The user can also search by diseases from the common cold to epilepsy to see the different types of medicines that are used to treat the respective illness and their costs relative to one another.
